trans-unit.source: Implement to participate in the creation or choosing of a <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName> object, especially to enable shared sessions.
trans-unit.target: Implementer delta i oppretting eller velge for en <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName> objektet, spesielt for å aktivere delte økter.

trans-unit.source: Implement the IInstanceContextProvider interface to provide the appropriate <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName> object to the system.
trans-unit.target: Implementere grensesnittet IInstanceContextProvider for å angi riktig <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName>objekt i systemet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Typically, this interface is implemented to support shared sessions, enable service instance pooling, control lifetimes of service instances, or to group contexts among clients.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis implementeres dette grensesnittet for å støtte delte økter aktivere tjenesten forekomsten utvalg, kontrollerer levetid for forekomster av tjenesten, eller til gruppen kontekster mellom klienter.

trans-unit.source: For example, to implement sharing, insert a custom IInstanceContextProvider to decide which session or call from a client is associated with which <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel for å implementere deler, setter du en egendefinert IInstanceContextProvider for å avgjøre hvilke økten eller kall fra en klient er knyttet til som <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: For an example that demonstrates the sharing of instance contexts, see [InstanceContextSharing](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/4a6a46d7-b7d7-4bb5-a0dd-03ffa3cbc230).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du for eksempel som demonstrerer deling av forekomst kontekster se [InstanceContextSharing](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/4a6a46d7-b7d7-4bb5-a0dd-03ffa3cbc230).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When an IInstanceContextProvider is inserted into [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], the normal property that controls the creation of <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> objects (the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property) is no longer checked and has no effect.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når en IInstanceContextProvider settes inn i [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], normal egenskapen som kontrollerer oppretting av <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekter (den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen) er ikke lenger sjekket og har ingen virkning.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: A more generic mechanism by which you can initialize <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> objects when created (for example, to attach custom extensions to each <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>) is the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextInitializer?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: En mer generell mekanisme som du kan starte <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekter under (for eksempel for å knytte tilpassede utvidelser til hver <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>) er <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextInitializer?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextInitializer?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: Called when a new message is received.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når en ny melding er mottatt.

trans-unit.source: The GetExistingInstanceContext method is called when a message is received.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetExistingInstanceContext kalles når en melding er mottatt.

trans-unit.source: Return the <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object that you want to process the message, or `null`.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekt som du vil behandle meldingen, eller `null`.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: In the case of `null`, [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] creates a new <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object for the message and then calls the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.InitializeInstanceContext%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Med `null`, [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] oppretter en ny <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekt for melding og kall den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.InitializeInstanceContext%2A>metoden.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.InitializeInstanceContext%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: If you return `null`, the new <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object goes through the throttling system and increments the count of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentInstances%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du går tilbake `null`, den nye <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet går gjennom båndbredderegulering systemet og øker antall <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentInstances%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentInstances%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: The incoming message.
trans-unit.target: Den innkommende meldingen.

trans-unit.source: The channel that received the message.
trans-unit.target: Kanalen som fikk meldingen.

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName> objekt som brukes til å behandle meldingen; returnerer <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> å be [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] til å opprette en ny <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: InitializeInstanceContext is called when <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.GetExistingInstanceContext%2A> returns `null` and a new <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object is created.
trans-unit.target: InitializeInstanceContext kalles når <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.GetExistingInstanceContext%2A>returnerer `null` og en ny <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekt er opprettet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.GetExistingInstanceContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: This method is called to notify you that a new <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> has been created.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles for å varsle deg som en ny <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>har blitt opprettet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.target: Den nye <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName> objektet.

trans-unit.target: Den innkommende meldingen.

trans-unit.source: The channel that received the message.
trans-unit.target: Kanalen som fikk meldingen.

trans-unit.source: Called when all <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> activities have completed to enable implementers to prevent the <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> from being recycled.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når alle <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>aktiviteter er fullført for å aktivere implementers å hindre at den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>fra resirkuleres.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: IsIdle is called when [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] is about to close and recycle an idle <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object so that you can inform the runtime whether to continue doing so.
trans-unit.target: IsIdle kalles når [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] er i ferd med å lukke og starte en inaktiv <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet slik at du kan informere kjøretiden om du vil fortsette å gjøre so.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: For an example that demonstrates the sharing of instance contexts, see [InstanceContextSharing](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/4a6a46d7-b7d7-4bb5-a0dd-03ffa3cbc230).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du for eksempel som demonstrerer deling av forekomst kontekster se [InstanceContextSharing](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/4a6a46d7-b7d7-4bb5-a0dd-03ffa3cbc230).

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object that is considered idle.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet anses som inaktiv.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] is to close and recycle the <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object and adjust the value of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentInstances%2A?displayProperty=fullName>; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] er å lukke og starte den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekt og Juster <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentInstances%2A?displayProperty=fullName>; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: Called when the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle*> method returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to enable implementers to provide a callback to notify [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] when the <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object is finished.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle*>metoden returnerer <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> å aktivere implementers oppgi en tilbakeringing som skal varsles [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] når den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet er fullført.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle*>

trans-unit.source: The NotifyIdle method is called when the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle%2A> method returns `false` to enable you to provide [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] with a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.InstanceContextIdleCallback?displayProperty=fullName> object that you use to inform the runtime that the <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> has finished its work.
trans-unit.target: Metoden NotifyIdle kalles når den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle%2A>metoden returnerer `false` slik at du kan angi [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] med en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.InstanceContextIdleCallback?displayProperty=fullName>objekt du bruker for å informere kjøretiden som den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>arbeidet er ferdig.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.InstanceContextIdleCallback?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.InstanceContextIdleCallback?displayProperty=fullName> object notifies the runtime that the <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> has finished its work, [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] calls <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle%2A> once again.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.InstanceContextIdleCallback?displayProperty=fullName>objektet varsler kjøretiden som den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>er ferdig med arbeidet, [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] kall <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle%2A>på nytt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.InstanceContextIdleCallback?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This cycle continues until <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle%2A> returns `true` and the context is closed and recycled.
trans-unit.target: Denne syklusen fortsetter før <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle%2A>returnerer `true` og konteksten er lukket resirkulert.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IInstanceContextProvider.IsIdle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.InstanceContextIdleCallback"></xref> object that notifies [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] when the <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object is to be closed and recycled.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.InstanceContextIdleCallback"> </xref> objektet som varsler [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] når den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet er lukket og resirkulert.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>
